translate indonesian tyan_falos_4_ea077d3f:
    # mc "Here's your frog."
    mc "Ini kataknya."

translate indonesian tyan_falos_4_a28f599c:
    # "Woah!"
    "Woah!"

translate indonesian tyan_falos_4_0214ead7:
    # "Apparently, you are very serious about this room rearrangement, since you needed a tape measure THAT badly."
    "Rupanya Kakak serius banget soal menata ulang kamar ini, sampai butuh meteran separah ITU."

translate indonesian tyan_falos_4_0fcd947e:
    # mc "It's also a good reason to help you get your thing back."
    mc "Ini juga alasan bagus buat bantu Kakak mendapatkan barang Kakak kembali."

translate indonesian tyan_falos_4_de8756ec:
    # "Hee hee hee! You're right. Thank you."
    "Hee hee hee! Kamu benar. Makasih."

translate indonesian tyan_falos_4_5bf3f7b0:
    # "I'll call her one of these days and pick up the tape measure."
    "Nanti aku akan meneleponnya dan mengambil meteran itu."

translate indonesian strings:
    old "Подождать 2 дня, прежде чем я смогу получить линейку у Кристи."
    new "Tunggu 2 hari sebelum aku bisa mendapatkan meteran dari Kak Christie."
